INTRODUCTION:
The project employee management system using C manages employee records using the file system.
This help to register employee, display all list of an employee on the screen, search a particular employee record, modify and delete information of an employee.
OBJECTIVES:
This project aims to simplify the task of maintaining records of the employees of Company.
To develop an well-designed database to store employee information.
Provides full functional reports to management of Company.
The objective of this project is to provide a comprehensive approach towards the management of employee information.
FEATURES:
Add record
List record
Modify record
Delete record
FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS:
AUTHENTICATION:
login
logout
login failure
AUTHORIZATION:
user role check
PROCESS DATA:
display 
edit
search
LEAVE APPLICATION/APPROVAL:
leave application
leave approval
NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS:
performance requirements
relaibility
scalibility


